mmgal - a program for creating static image galleries
Copyright 2007-2009 Marcin Owsiany <marcin@owsiany.pl>

Supported backend image information libraries
=============================================

The program works with either Image::ExifTool or Image::Info. However
Image::ExifTool is recommended, and Image::Info is only supported on a
"best-effort" basis. (In fact the Image::Info documentation states that
Image::ExifTool is a better and less buggy library.)

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Performance comparison with imageindex:
=======================================

Gallery: 15GB of 9100 images in 528 folders

imageindex:
 - generating a gallery from scratch:
    9414.61user 919.38system 2:59:02elapsed 96%CPU (0avgtext+0avgdata 0maxresident)k
    0inputs+0outputs (174425major+226765997minor)pagefaults 0swaps
 - on a freshly generated gallery:
    2342.84user 437.39system 51:48.89elapsed 89%CPU (0avgtext+0avgdata 0maxresident)k
    0inputs+0outputs (155159major+103164844minor)pagefaults 0swaps


mmgal
