----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Some useful commands:
=====================

diff -u <(find * -type f|LANG=C sort) <(LANG=C sort MANIFEST )
grep pm$ MANIFEST |xgettext --add-comments=TRANSLATORS: --copyright-holder="Marcin Owsiany <marcin@owsiany.pl>" -d mmgal -o po/mmgal.pot.new -f -
mv po/mmgal.pot po/mmgal.pot.old
msgmerge po/mmgal.pot.old po/mmgal.pot.new > po/mmgal.pot

